<view class="login-page">
  <!-- 品牌区 -->
  <view class="login-brand">
    <image class="brand-illustration" src="../../../assets/auth/img-login.png" mode="widthFix" />
  </view>

  <!-- 表单区 -->
  <view class="login-form">
    <view class="field-group">
      <view class="field-heading">
        <text class="field-label">账号</text>
        <text class="field-tip">初次登录会直接创建账号，请记住自己的账号哦～</text>
      </view>
      <input
        class="login-input"
        type="nickname"
        placeholder="请输入账号"
        placeholder-class="login-placeholder"
        data-field="username"
        bindinput="onInput"
        bindfocus="onUsernameFocus"
        bindconfirm="submitLogin"
        confirm-type="done"
        value="{{username}}"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="login-buttons">
      <app-button text="登录" variant="dark" width-mode="full" loading="{{isSubmitting}}" disabled="{{isSubmitting}}" bind:press="submitLogin" />

      <app-button variant="light" width-mode="full" disabled="{{isSubmitting}}" bind:press="showAbout">
        <image slot="prefix" class="info-icon" src="../../../assets/auth/info-o.svg" mode="aspectFit" />
        <text class="login-about-text">关于家物小记</text>
      </app-button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- 关于家物小记 - 底部弹出面板 -->
  <view class="about-mask {{aboutVisible ? 'about-mask--show' : ''}}" wx:if="{{aboutShow}}" bindtap="hideAbout">
    <view class="about-panel {{aboutVisible ? 'about-panel--show' : ''}}" catchtap="noop">
      <!-- 导航栏 -->
      <view class="about-navbar">
        <view class="about-navbar__left" bindtap="hideAbout">
          <image class="about-close-icon" src="../../../assets/auth/cross.svg" mode="aspectFit" />
        </view>
        <view class="about-navbar__title">关于家物小记</view>
        <view class="about-navbar__right"></view>
      </view>

      <!-- 内容区（可滚动） -->
      <scroll-view class="about-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}">
        <view class="about-video-wrap">
          <video
            wx:if="{{aboutVideoReady}}"
            id="login-about-video"
            class="about-video"
            src="{{aboutVideoUrl}}"
            poster="{{aboutPosterUrl}}"
            controls="{{true}}"
            show-center-play-btn="{{true}}"
            enable-play-gesture="{{true}}"
            object-fit="cover"
            bindplay="onAboutVideoPlay"
            bindpause="onAboutVideoPause"
            bindended="onAboutVideoEnded"
          />
          <view wx:if="{{aboutVideoReady && !aboutVideoPlaying}}" class="about-video-overlay" catchtap="playAboutVideo">
            <view class="about-video-overlay__button">
              <view class="about-video-overlay__triangle"></view>
            </view>
          </view>
          <image wx:else class="about-video" src="{{aboutPosterUrl || '../../../assets/auth/img-login.png'}}" mode="aspectFill" />
        </view>

        <!-- 介绍文字 -->
        <view class="about-text">
          <text>亲爱的朋友，你是否在生活中有过这样的场景：\n\n“诶？我们家的用电户号是多少来着？我记得之前办理开户时那个单子上有，但那个单子放哪儿去了？”\n\n“诶？我们家那个车位产权证号是多少来着？还有车位详细产权地址是什么？办理这个业务要咋这么多信息？我现在上哪儿找去？”\n\n“这里要填车架号，车架号不行驶证上才有么？但行驶证在家里咋弄呢？”\n\n“这热水器出问题了，报错E1是什么意思呀？之前热水器的说明书放哪儿去了？”\n\n“这一抽屉的说明书太碍事儿了，平时又不用，要用了又要找很久，找到还要翻阅很久，太麻烦了”\n\n“诶？我们家毛毛当时从宠物店抱回来时那个出生证呢？我想看下他出生日期”\n\n............\n\n现在有了【家物小记】这些问题都能轻松解决，你只需要把他们拍下来，识别一下，一个图文并茂的专属记忆就存下来了。\n你可以随时查看，还能通过搜索在记忆列表、记忆详情中快速找到你想要的内容～～</text>
        </view>
      </scroll-view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
